ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This semester everyone in HIST 874 has made great contribution to the seminar. I would recommend this course to students who enjoy heavy but interesting reading materials and who want to conduct insightful historical research related to East Asia.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The professor allows students to conduct a research on any topic related to East Asia. The reading assignments are really helpful in terms of methodology. It is especially useful for me preparation for the Master's thesis.
It really shows me how to be professional as a reader, writer, and a scholar.
